{"sn17.22:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 17.22 ","sn17.22:0.2":"3. Tatiyavagga ","sn17.22:0.3":"Kalyanisutta ","sn17.22:1.1":"Savatthiyam viharati. ","sn17.22:1.2":"“Daruno, bhikkhave, labhasakkarasiloko …pe… ","sn17.22:1.3":"na tassa, bhikkhave, janapadakalyani eka ekassa cittam pariyadaya titthati yassa labhasakkarasiloko cittam pariyadaya titthati. ","sn17.22:1.4":"Evam daruno kho, bhikkhave, labhasakkarasiloko …pe… ","sn17.22:1.5":"evanhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. ","sn17.22:1.6":"Dutiyam. "}